title: New Details Layout
message:
New Details Layout

	The CompassView also got an update, which now you can set the app:textSize attribute.

title: Fix on Tablet layout
message:
Fix on Tablet layout

	Now it also selects the first item by default on the Tablet.
	There are plenty of files edited because I renamed the package from 'example' to 'zelius'.

title: Correction on the Forecast Columns indexes
message: Correction on the Forecast Columns indexes

title: Add Daily Notifications
message:
Add Daily Notifications

	1. The app now sends notifications to users when it gets new data.
	2. Now it also removes old stored data that was accumulating.
	3. For Map Location it gets geo location from the adapter instead of SharedPreferences.

title: SyncAdapter implementation
message:
SyncAdapter implementation

	The SyncAdapter allows the app to schedule when to retrieve data from the cloud.

title: New custom view: compass
message:
New custom view: compass

	The compass shows the direction of the wind on the DetailFragment.

title: Make Sunshine for Tablets
message:
Make Sunshine for Tablets

	For tablets there will be no DetailActivity since the details of the forecast will be shown through the same screen of the Forecast List with the DetailFragment.

message: Load Forecast Art based on WeatherConditionID
